00:02:03.860 --> 00:02:09.119
One of the great features about being injection
molded and not a homemade cut is that the

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:13.610
surface is perfectly flat which means your
shots are a lot straighter.

00:02:13.610 --> 00:02:14.640
Also the same with the caps.

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:20.200
The caps are so flat that your shots are going
to be a lot more accurate so the mallet heads

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:22.460
